---

<ResearchPageTemplate
  title="Nutrition Clinical Research"
  metaTitle="Nutrition Research | Central Dentist"
  description="Essential reading on nutrition and its profound impact on oral and systemic health. Discover evidence-based approaches to optimal wellness through diet."
>
  <div slot="introduction">
    <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary mb-6">
      The Foundation of Health: Nutrition
    </h2>
    <p class="text-body-large mb-8">
      Your diet is the foundation of your health. What you eat directly affects not only your oral health,
      but your brain function, energy levels, immune system, and risk of chronic disease. These essential
      books provide evidence-based insights into the powerful connection between nutrition and wellness.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div slot="main-content">
    <div class="bg-teal-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8" style="border-left: 4px solid #0099ba;">
      <p class="text-body-regular font-semibold" style="color: #006786;">
        Dr. Weston Price's groundbreaking research demonstrated that traditional, nutrient-dense diets
        led to perfect dental arches, minimal decay, and exceptional overall healthâ€”validating the
        inseparable connection between nutrition and oral wellness.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section slot="studies-section" class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary text-center mb-4">
            Essential Reading on Nutrition
          </h2>
          <p class="text-section-subheader text-center mb-12">
            Books that transform our understanding of food and health
          </p>
        </BlurFade>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          {books.map((book, index) => (
            <BlurFade delay={200 + (index * 50)}>
              <Card className="p-6">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
                  {book.image && (
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                      <img
                        src={book.image}
                        alt={`${book.title} book cover`}
                        class="w-full md:w-48 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md"
                        loading="lazy"
                      />
                    </div>
                  )}
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <h3 class="text-card-header mb-3" style="color: #006786;">
                      {book.title}
                    </h3>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                      <a
                        href={book.authorUrl}
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-sm hover:underline"
                        style="color: #0099ba;"
                      >
                        ðŸ“– Author: {book.author}
                      </a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-body-regular mb-4">
                      {book.summary}
                    </p>
                    <a
                      href={book.sourceUrl}
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a6b443] to-[#c7cd85] text-white rounded-full text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:from-[#8fa339] hover:to-[#a6b443] hover:shadow-lg"
                    >
                      View on Amazon
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </Card>
            </BlurFade>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div slot="related-links">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <BlurFade delay={200}>
        <a href="/clinical-research/fluoride-free-prevention" class="block">
          <Card className="h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-card-header mb-3">Fluoride-Free Prevention</h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular">
                Research on natural approaches to cavity prevention.
              </p>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </a>
      </BlurFade>

      <BlurFade delay={300}>
        <a href="/clinical-research/growth-and-development" class="block">
          <Card className="h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-card-header mb-3">Growth & Development</h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular">
                The role of nutrition in proper facial and dental development.
              </p>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </a>
      </BlurFade>

      <BlurFade delay={400}>
        <a href="/philosophy" class="block">
          <Card className="h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-card-header mb-3">Our Philosophy</h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular">
                Learn about our holistic approach to dental care.
              </p>
            </div>
